text: National Highway 143B, commonly referred to as NH 143B is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 43. NH-143B runs in the states of Chhattisgarh and Jharkhand in India. == Route == NH143B connects Jashpur Nagar, Jagannathpur, Gobindpur, Dumri and Mahuadanr in the states of Chhattisgarh and Jharkhand. == Junctions == : Terminal near Jashpur Nagar. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Jharkhand Category:National Highways in Chhattisgarh
